OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FBy ITV News Correspondent Sejal Karia,
OL,7,FSenior Producer Eleanor Gregory and
OL,8,FSenior Producer Louisa Felton
OL,10,FA senior paramedic, a university
OL,11,Ftechnician and the former boss of a
OL,12,Ffootball club are among 13 men charged
OL,13,Falongside a husband accused of
OL,14,Fconspiring to drug and sexually abuse
OL,15,Fhis unconscious wife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
