PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FAll 13 can today be named for the
OL,7,Ffirst time, after reporting
OL,8,Frestrictions on identifying the men,
OL,9,Fwho are from across the UK, were
OL,10,Flifted ahead of a trial due to start
OL,11,Fin Manchester in September.
OL,13,FITV News is not naming the husband at
OL,14,Fthe centre of the case so as not to
OL,15,Fidentify his wife, who is protected by
OL,16,Fanonymity under British law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FHe is in his 60's and from the
OL,7,FStockport area, Greater Manchester and
OL,8,Fhas been charged with 48 offences
OL,9,Fwhich allege he drugged his wife to
OL,10,Frape and sexually assault her on his
OL,11,Fown over more than twenty years since
OL,12,F2004.
OL,14,FThe identities of 13 other men, aged
OL,15,Fbetween 28 and 73, who face charges
OL,16,Frelating to the same alleged victim
OL,17,Fcan now be reported for the first time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
