PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FKeith Fotheringham, 59, from Dundee,
OL,7,Fhas pleaded guilty to all four sexual
OL,8,Foffences against him, including
OL,9,Fconspiracy to rape and conspiracy to
OL,10,Fadminister a substance. He is in
OL,11,Fcustody and will be sentenced at a
OL,12,Flater date.
OL,14,FThe other 12 men have pleaded not
OL,15,Fguilty to the various charges against
OL,16,Fthem and face trial alongside the
OL,17,Fhusband, later this year, in
OL,18,FManchester's Minshull Street Crown
OL,19,FCourt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
