CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FJonathan Kirk, 43, a senior paramedic,
OL,7,Fdenies charges including rape and
OL,8,Fconspiracy to rape. He is on bail.
OL,10,FKirk was pictured with Prince Harry in
OL,11,F2011 during a visit to the Salford
OL,12,FAmbulance Station in the wake of the
OL,13,F2011 UK riots.
OL,15,FFormer CEO of Taunton Town Football
OL,16,FClub, Karl Lindsay, resigned from his
OL,17,Frole at the time of his arrest in
OL,18,FNovember 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
