PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FLindsay has denied all the charges
OL,7,Fagainst him, including conspiracy to
OL,8,Frape and conspiracy to administer a
OL,9,Fsubstance with intent to stupefy or
OL,10,Foverpower to allow sexual activity. He
OL,11,Fis in custody.
OL,13,FDaniel Rayner, 42, of Whitstable,
OL,14,FKent, and David Graves, 59, of
OL,15,FIlkeston, Derbyshire, have denied the
OL,16,Fsame charges. Both are in custody.
OL,18,FGraham Brougham, 73 of Northwich,
OL,19,FCheshire, has pleaded not guilty to
OL,20,Fcharges including rape and conspiracy
OL,21,Fto rape. He is on bail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
