OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FPhilip Wild, 58, of Stockport, Greater
OL,7,FManchester, has pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fcharges including attempted rape,
OL,9,Fsexual assault and conspiracy to rape.
OL,10,FHe is in custody.
OL,12,FMohammed Sabir, 28, of Stockport,
OL,13,Fdenies the charges against him
OL,14,Fincluding three counts of rape and
OL,15,Fconspiracy to rape. He is in custody.
OL,17,FSean Peers, 37, of Stockport, has
OL,18,Fpleaded not guilty to assault by
OL,19,Fpenetration and conspiracy to assault
OL,20,Fby penetration. He is on bail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
