OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FJordan Wallace, 31, of Wythenshawe,
OL,7,FManchester, has pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Frape, attempted rape and conspiracy to
OL,9,Frape. He is on bail.
OL,11,FAlan Keelan, 42, of Wythenshawe, who
OL,12,Fused to coach an under-16s football
OL,13,Fteam and is from Greater Manchester
OL,14,Fdenies conspiracy to rape and two
OL,15,Fcounts of rape.
OL,17,FHe is on bail and Robert Stewart, 70,
OL,18,Fof Stockport, also denies the same
OL,19,Fcharges and he is in custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
