OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FRichard Townsend, 37, of Heywood,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, denies assault by
OL,8,Fpenetration and conspiracy to assault
OL,9,Fby penetration. He is also in custody.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the husband, who cannot be
OL,17,Fidentified, changed some of his pleas
OL,18,Fafter he previously denied all 48
OL,19,Fcounts he faced on the indictment
OL,20,Finvolving his wife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
