OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to five counts of
OL,7,Frape, six counts of assault by
OL,8,Fpenetration and three counts of sexual
OL,9,Fassault on various dates between 2022
OL,10,Fand 2025.
OL,12,FHe has also admitted to sharing
OL,13,Fintimate photographs or film of his
OL,14,Fwife, without her consent, for sexual
OL,15,Fgratification.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
