PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FBetween 2018 and his arrest in 2025,
OL,7,Fhe is also accused of plotting with
OL,8,Fother men to sexually assault and rape
OL,9,Fhis wife while she was unconscious and
OL,10,Finvited them to carry out the attacks
OL,11,Falongside him. He has pleaded not
OL,12,Fguilty to these offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
