PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782609481
OL,3,CNames released of 13 men charged with
OL,4,Csex abuse of woman 'drugged by husband'
OL,6,FHe denies 11 counts of rape, two
OL,7,Fcounts of attempted rape, seven counts
OL,8,Fof assault by penetration, four counts
OL,9,Fof sexual assault, four counts of
OL,10,Fconspiracy to rape, three counts of
OL,11,Fconspiracy to assault by penetration,
OL,12,Fone count of conspiracy to administer
OL,13,Fa substance with intent and one count
OL,14,Fof administering a substance with
OL,15,Fintent.
OL,17,FAll of the men, apart from Keith
OL,18,FFotheringham, are due to stand trial
OL,19,Fon 1st September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
